{"tid":1696490,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"九巴司機被無理指控阻差辦公　向警務處長索償　警方申撤銷申索","createTime":"2019-11-06T07:58:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T12:37:13.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"89aad9c52f21bfe29c755eeec604652186252096","tid":1696490,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T07:58:43.000Z","msg":"兩名青年今年 9 月 14 日於牛頭角樂華邨巴士站遭便衣警員制服及拘捕，目擊事件的九巴司機要求警員出示委任證，但卻被指阻差辦公，司機其後指警員無理指摘和威脅，令他情緒不穩及當天無法工作，早前入稟小額錢債審裁處，向警務處處長追討1萬港元賠償。案件今（6 日）再提訊，警務處一方指司機並無理據索償，向法庭申請撤銷申索，審裁官押後案件至明年 2 月 5 日再訊，以待雙方準備證人供詞等。<br />\n<br />\n申索人為陳詠麟，被告則為警務處處長盧偉聰。審裁官向陳表示，涉及政府部門的申索，均由律政司派出代表應訊，故他應將被告人改為由律政司司長。陳又表示他事後曾向精神科醫生求診等，審裁官則要求他於證人供詞中交代事件及提供醫療報告。警務處一方則指，即使法庭接納申索人就事件的說法，警方亦並無對他造成任何可申索的傷害，認為他沒有理據進行索償，故申請剔除申索。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E8%A2%AB%E7%84%A1%E7%90%86%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E9%98%BB%E5%B7%AE%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC-%E5%90%91%E8%AD%A6%E5%8B%99%E8%99%95%E9%95%B7%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E7%94%B3%E6%92%A4%E9%8A%B7%E7%94%B3%E7%B4%A2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2585%25AC-%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258B%2599%25E8%2599%2595%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%2584%259F-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%2594%25B3%25E6%2592%25A4%25E9%258A%25B7%25E7%2594%25B3%25E7%25B4%25A2%2F&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnXzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=2388f253\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2585%25AC-%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258B%2599%25E8%2599%2595%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%2584%259F-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%2594%25B3%25E6%2592%25A4%25E9%258A%25B7%25E7%2594%25B3%25E7%25B4%25A2%2F&h=1e1d38af\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E8%A2%AB%E7%84%A1%E7%90%86%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E9%98%BB%E5%B7%AE%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC-%E5%90%91%E8%AD%A6%E5%8B%99%E8%99%95%E9%95%B7%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E7%94%B3%E6%92%A4%E9%8A%B7%E7%94%B3%E7%B4%A2/</a>"},{"pid":"2fde59417a29f6c74e766fd65fdd150c4cb4ed72","tid":1696490,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8760497653eb7b197744acd291a247f19e69daed","tid":1696490,"uid":278765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:37:13.000Z","msg":"九巴車長好波！"}]}